    if not user.is_admin:
        raise HTTPException(...)

# âœ… CORRECT
def check_admin(user: User) -> None:  # Explicitly None
    if not user.is_admin:
        raise HTTPException(...)
```

### 4. Wrong Literal Usage

```python
